Here you can find a collection of recipes and techniques to fine tune how you consume Vexilla.

## Polling

You will often want to update your flags during runtime rather than just on load. To set this up polling the JSON data is perfectly acceptable. The length of the interval is up to you and your needs. You can even poll for different flag groups independently at different intervals.

